{"tid":2062124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑人運動BLM訊求：黑人霸權","createTime":"2020-06-13T02:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T03:40:29.000Z","uid":270220,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b9a8b2fc01a51df2dacf22dfbc4be59289703d41","tid":2062124,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T02:23:36.000Z","msg":"Chanelle Helm 係其中一個運動始創人，訊求如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. White people, if you don&rsquo;t have any descendants, will your property to a black or brown family. Preferably one that lives in generational poverty. <br />\n<br />\n白人冇後代的話，遺產歸黑人。<br />\n<br />\n2. White people, if you&rsquo;re inheriting property you intend to sell upon acceptance, give it to a black or brown family. You&rsquo;re bound to make that money in some other white privileged way.<br />\n<br />\n想出售的遺產俾黑人。<br />\n<br />\n3. If you are a developer or realty owner of multi-family housing, build a sustainable complex in a black or brown blighted neighborhood and let black and brown people live in it for free.<br />\n<br />\n白人為黑人免費建造房屋。<br />\n<br />\n4. White people, if you can afford to downsize, give up the home you own to a black or brown family. Preferably a family from generational poverty.<br />\n<br />\n白人房屋俾黑人。<br />\n<br />\n5. White people, if any of the people you intend to leave your property to are racists a**holes, change the will, and will your property to a black or brown family. Preferably a family from generational poverty.<br />\n<br />\n都係將想出售的遺產俾黑人。<br />\n<br />\n6. White people, re-budget your monthly so you can donate to black funds for land purchasing.<br />\n<br />\n白人每月出錢俾黑人買地。<br />\n<br />\n7. White people, especially white women (because this is yaw specialty &mdash; Nosey Jenny and Meddling Kathy), get a racist fired. Yaw know what the f**k they be saying. You are complicit when you ignore them. Get your boss fired cause they racist too.<br />\n<br />\n炒種族主義者。<br />\n<br />\n8. Backing up No. 7, this should be easy but all those sheetless Klan, Nazi&rsquo;s and Other lil&rsquo; d**k-white men will all be returning to work. Get they a*s fired. Call the police even: they look suspicious.<br />\n<br />\n都係炒種族主義者。<br />\n<br />\n9. OK, backing up No. 8, if any white person at your work, or as you enter in spaces and you overhear a white person praising the actions from yesterday, first, get a pic. Get their name and more info. Hell, find out where they work &mdash; Get Them Fired. But certainly address them, and, if you need to, you got hands: use them.<br />\n<br />\n如上。。。<br />\n<br />\n10. Commit to two things: Fighting white supremacy where and how you can (this doesn&rsquo;t mean taking up knitting, unless you&rsquo;re making scarves for black and brown kids in need), and funding black and brown people and their work.<br />\n<br />\n打擊白人霸權，資助黑人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://truthuncensored.net/give-up-the-home-you-own-black-lives-matter-co-founder-makes-list-of-demands-for-white-people/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruthuncensored.net%2Fgive-up-the-home-you-own-black-lives-matter-co-founder-makes-list-of-demands-for-white-people%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=f0b60ead\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://truthuncensored.net/give-up-the-home-you-own-black-lives-matter-co-founder-makes-list-of-demands-for-white-people/</a>"},{"pid":"7b81ce548a6b93feba200fc2106264e730772832","tid":2062124,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T02:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d8774b7c21359c301fe7730ab56470841f5ac4","tid":2062124,"uid":198400,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講就係唔想做但又想要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkg